# Snake Game

## Features


# Siple Controls
Arrow Keys: Use the arrow keys to move the snake in four directions (up, down, left, right).
Q: Quit the game from the game-over screen.
C: Restart the game from the game-over screen.

# Difficulty Levels
Easy Mode: Perfect for beginners or a relaxed gameplay experience. The snake moves slower.
Hard Mode: For the challenge-seekers! The snake moves faster, demanding quick reflexes.

# Score Display
Your current score is displayed on the screen during gameplay.
See your final score after losing the game.

# Dynamic Graphics
Clean, simple visuals with distinct colors for the snake, food, and background.
Smooth animations for a pleasant gameplay experience.